arts.ttl: Götze reflects on Frankfurt role: "I feel like the grandpa here."

arts.ttl: Mario Götze clinches Eintracht Frankfurt victory over Werder Bremen
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt players, including Mario Götze, Hugo Ekitiké, and Marco Friedl, celebrate the crucial goal against SV Werder Bremen. Eintracht Frankfurt secured a comfortable 1-0 win over Werder Bremen on Saturday thanks to Mario Götze's lone strike.

arts.ttl: Can Eintracht Frankfurt win the Bundesliga?
arts.sum: Now heading into the international break sitting pretty following a four-game win streak in all competitions, it’s time bundesliga.com asked, are Eintracht Frankfurt title contenders? Heading into the November international break, Marmoush had scored five more goals than any Bundesliga player not named Kane, and it doesn’t look like he’ll be slowing down any time soon.

arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt vs. Werder Bremen preview: Die Adler looking to continue winning run
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt will look to claim a fifth consecutive victory in all competitions when they welcome Werder Bremen to Deutsche Bank Park for Saturday’s Bundesliga contest.
